# Configure AI Collaborators

<!--Add me to TOCs-->

<!--Add mentions to other AI Articles-->

AI Collaborators are a way to onboard AI agents into your projects and tasks. You can configure an AI Collaborator with the workflow that you want it to perform, then assign it to a task as you would a user.

Currently, AI Collaborators can be used to review content. More AI Collaborator capabilities will be available in the future.


